Q. Can we return table from a function??


	CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION table_1() RETURNS varchar AS'
	DECLARE 
		srec student%ROWTYPE;
	BEGIN
		select * INTO srec 
		from student;
		
		return 1;
	
	END;
	'LANGUAGE 'plpgsql';
	
	
	
	
	
	
